Package: BasicStatsByC
Title: Basic (Bayesian) Statistic functions 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Chanyoung", "Woo", , "c.woo@camppus.lmu.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: BasicStatsByC provides basic functions for statistical analysis and Bayesian statistics, including summary statistics, t-tests, chi-square tests, linear regression, Bayesian t-tests, Bayesian linear regression, and Bayesian correlation. A few of those functions comes with a (optional) plot. 
